Text.string: Lorelei sent me. What's up with the diner?
Lorelei sent me. I'm here to help.
I am here by the request of Lorelei.
Here to help, boyo. Lorelei sent me.
Okay, so, those fascist Maliwan bastards are using MY DINER to supply THEIR troops! Stop them! Go on, do it! Kill 'em all!
BUMMER! The digistructor's out of meat samples! We can't digistruct any Dynasty Burgers without meat samples! Okay. I need you to bring me a sample of my secret ingredient: ratch meat.
Trust, my dude! I know it sounds vile, but it makes the burgers so damn JUICY! There's a ratch den in the trash pit. Go get 'em!
In the mean time, Vault Hunter, could you deliver that burger to Lorelei for me?
Proper kudos for taking out Captain Rowe, Vault Hunter. That burger-grubbing prick has been a right thorn in my ass. But now he's dead. Well done indeed.
Just hit the button!
Buttons for burgers!
Gotta hit that button!
Press the button!
Yes! Now bring it back to me!
Yes! A new burger is born! Haha! Okay. Now we need a delivery bot so we can get these burgers to the people who need 'em! Hit that button!
Now, start by squishing some ratch larva! Doing that should draw out the angry momma ratch. And THAT'S where you'll get a big ol' ratch steak. Mmm, mmm, MMM! Juicy.
Did Lorelei send you?!
Now digiscan that big hunk of disgusting, delicious meat!
What?! Chase after it! Just—follow the trail of burgers! Gahh, what a waste!
Burger bots aren't designed for combat, so he's glitching out! Take out those Maliwan to get him moving again!
Encountering hostile area. Recalibrating route.
Ach, more Maliwan! Take 'em out to get the burger bot moving again!

When Maliwan showed up, I barricaded myself in my apartment. And I'm not coming out until this war is over, you hear me?! But YOU can help me get the diner up and running, and I can run it remotely from here!
Hostile area cleared. Continuing route.
Pick up that burger the bot dropped!
It's burger time for Lorelei! Well, it WILL be, once you bring her that burger!
Come on! Pick up that burger before it gets cold!
Go on! Pick up that burger!
Yes! Hell yes! I can finally get back to doing what I love: making some freakin' burgers! Burgers are LIFE, my dude.
Press the button!
Press iiiit!
Button! BUTTON!
Button.
Oh no, I've said it too many times, and now the word “button” no longer has any meaning at all!
Button.
Burger bot! What up, my dude?! High-five!
Negative.
What?! Chase after it!
Whatever you say, little man.
Uh... heh. Sure they are.
I hear good things about these... “burgers”.
You're tellin' me!
Hey, hey! Burger time! I'll be right down, little guy!
NOW! GET THAT WANKER!
Hey! Hey you! I need help, dammit!
Come on! Let's go! It's time to get the diner up and running!
Put the meat on the digiscanner so we can DO THIS THING!
Got another job for you, Vault Hunter.
Error. Insufficient meat data for: “burgers”.
I need to keep my people fed.

Now that we've got coffee, priority number two is food. Maliwan recently took over the Dynasty Diner, which WAS pumping out food for our people before it got taken. Go find the owner, Beau, and help him take his diner back.
And, on a personal note... there's this Maliwan guy, Captain Rowe, who's been giving me no end of trouble. I haven't been able to pin him down, but I hear he's got a serious weakness for burgers.
Beau, it's me. And I've got hungry people back at the base, you get me?
Unnngh! I get you, Lorelei! I so get you!
Let's go!
Let's go get 'em!
We're still not clear! Finish off those Maliwan bastards!
I'm still seeing Maliwan! Take 'em out!
Ugh! You gotta take out ALL the Maliwan around the diner!
Kick those Maliwan fascists outta my diner! All of 'em!
Ghhh... what?!
Guhh. You can't be serious.
Are those things even edible by your kind?
Ughhh, that's just wrong.
Grab a hunk of meat!
The meat! Grab it!
Go on! Pick up that meat!
Come on! Pick up the meat!
Good work! Here comes the big one!
There you go! Now grab a big hunk of that disgusting, delicious meat!
Priority One Directive: Deliver burgers to Maliwan Captain Archer Rowe.
Lorelei! My burger bot is trying to deliver a meal to that Captain Rowe guy you were talkin' about!
What? You're joking! Vault Hunter, follow the bot! This is our chance to get that Maliwan bastard!
Burger delivery for Captain Archer Rowe.
It wasn't... burger time...
It wasn't burger time! It wasn't burger time at all...
Nice job takin' out that high-value target, Vault Hunter!
Lorelei, it's gonna take some time to override Maliwan's control over my burger bots, and this one might as well be scrap, so... bye, burger bot!
Digistructing: “burgers”.
Lorelei! I'm sending the first of many burgers your way! Just need some time to reprogram my burger bots, then I'll be back on my burger-slingin' feet!
Much appreciated, Beau! Keep 'em comin'! We got a lot of hungry people back here.
First coffee, now burgers. The cornerstones of civilization! Piece by piece, we're really starting to put this city back together. Thanks for your help.
Okay, here we are. Let's get some new burgers going! Hit that button and digistruct those big bad burgers! Yeah!
